Diapensiaceae

Galax urceolata (Poir.) Brummitt

United States, Virginia, Giles County. Mountain Lake Biological Station.
Roadbed outside of MLBS_R_006. Vicinity of NEON plot MLBS_R_006.
37.42860 N, -80.56321 W. WGS84. 777 m.

Grassy roadbed in an oak/pine forest. Associated with *Quercus alba*,
*Vaccinium stamineum*, *Gaultheria procumbens*, *Lycopodium obscurum*, and
*Viola* sp.

Flowering.
